### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@projectSlug = my-awesome-portfolio
# After you run the POST request, copy the ID from the response and paste it here
@projectId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
# A valid UUID from your media_assets table
@thumbnailId = 0055af03-ff0b-4ed1-9773-409b4a7c2a1a

// ==========================================
// 1. PROJECT RETRIEVAL
// ==========================================

### ‚úÖ Get All Projects
# Maps to: GET /api/projects/
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json



### üîó Get Project By Slug
# Maps to: GET /api/projects/slug/:slug
# This also increments the view count in the background
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/slug/{{projectSlug}}
Content-Type: application/json



### üÜî Get Project By ID
# Maps to: GET /api/projects/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json



### üîç Get Project with Thumbnail Details
# Maps to: GET /api/projects/:id/details
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/details
Content-Type: application/json


// ==========================================
// 2. PROJECT MANAGEMENT (ADMIN)
// ==========================================

### ‚úçÔ∏è Create New Project
# Maps to: POST /api/projects/
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Awesome Portfolio",
  "slug": "my-awesome-portfolio",
  "mainDescription": "A high-performance portfolio built with Node.js, Drizzle, and UUIDs.",
  "mainThumbnailId": "{{thumbnailId}}",
  "status": "published",
  "isFeatured": true
}



### üîÑ Update Project
# Maps to: PUT /api/projects/:id
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Portfolio Title",
  "isFeatured": false,
  "status": "archived"
}



### ‚ùå Delete Project
# Maps to: DELETE /api/projects/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json